{"tid":2045989,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(段皇爺) 五間大學校長發聲明指理解訂立港區國安法必要性","createTime":"2020-06-01T06:35:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T06:35:09.000Z","uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4cb9adf4ffb41ddd8cd860eeb11490650a59af39","tid":2045989,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:35:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392920&d=jFWDEiyvEellqADaqpERGkV6NNh9RYlaag4wFuTDRgw%3D&h=761286d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D392920&h=2e9e5ee1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=392920</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】本港五間大學校長發聲明，表示理解訂立港區國安法的必要性。<br />\n<br />\n嶺南大學校長<span style=\"color: red;\">鄭國漢</span>、中文大學校長<span style=\"color: red;\">段崇智</span>、教育大學校長<span style=\"color: red;\">張仁良</span>、理工大學校長<span style=\"color: red;\">滕錦光</span>、香港大學校長<span style=\"color: red;\">張翔</span>發聲明，指國家及香港的繁榮穩定，與青年人的未來息息相關，安全穩定社會環境、健全法制與法治、良好治安、多元包容，對香港長遠發展至為重要。<br />\n<br />\n他們表示完全支持一國兩制，理解訂立國家安全法的必要性，並珍惜《基本法》所保障的言論、新聞、出版及集會自由，將一如既往堅守學術自由、卓越教研及院校自主，並維護多元文化，貢獻社會。<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------<br />\n其他四個本身係仆街唔駛理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}